e=2022-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220306033428/https://china.huanqiu.com/article/45Z4iUUAr32 |dead-url=no }}</ref>11月30日，全长20.287公里，位于线路施工难度最大地段的福厦高铁泉州湾跨海大桥全桥贯通。<ref>{{cite web |title=新建福厦铁路泉州湾跨海大桥全桥贯通 |url=http://www.news.cn/politics/2021-11/30/c_1128116005.htm |website=新华网 |publisher=新华社 |accessdate=2021-11-30 |date=2021-11-30 |archive-date=2021-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211130170357/http://www.news.cn/politics/2021-11/30/c_1128116005.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

